stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RequestReceived
    RequestReceived --> MLMode: ML ответил < 3 сек и confidence высокий
    RequestReceived --> FallbackMode: ML недоступен или timeout
    RequestReceived --> HybridMode: часть ML-ответа полезна, часть слабая

    MLMode --> ResponseReturned
    FallbackMode --> ResponseReturned
    HybridMode --> ResponseReturned

    ResponseReturned --> [*]
